{"tid":1210192,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家唔好畀非黑即白嘅邏輯誤導","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T22:27:39.000Z","uid":88263,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e090295a2ee8e734ebbcb86242c9f053a3345386","tid":1210192,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:15:18.000Z","msg":"你熱愛返工嘅，假設你係返立法會，假設全港大塞車，地鐵全綫訊號故障，請你行路都繼續行去立法會返工<br />\n<br />\n你唔熱愛返工，唔中意刺激，熱愛旅遊、遊車河嘅，請守法體驗一流港鐵服務<br />\n<br />\n[香港命脈][野餐以外]一星期暢遊港鐵體驗包 [鐵膠推介]<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1205357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1205357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n到時候原本瞓緊嘅、扮瞓嘅都會畀你嘈醒<br />\n<br />\n世界唔係非黑即白，亦唔係周街鬼，假設你藍田出發想去金鐘，你搭鐵可以綠綫轉紅綫，又可以紫綫轉藍綫，去到金鐘就OK。"},{"pid":"b373b1266b6fe4f65adb6ff7013a739859ca7f6e","tid":1210192,"uid":132283,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:19:19.000Z","msg":"請問點解要拖慢想出金鐘嘅人"},{"pid":"d863e9ab5fafe281a99f9e1aec7d551678319d39","tid":1210192,"uid":87745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:21:47.000Z","msg":"到時只會被瞓緊教同扮瞓既屌柒<br />\n正如今日d司機屌晒鬼一樣"},{"pid":"2801c98cc451fae9ddaac8da5457a2a33bc6768b","tid":1210192,"uid":44646,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"b373b1266b6fe4f65adb6ff7013a739859ca7f6e","tid":1210192,"uid":132283,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:19:19.000Z","msg":"請問點解要拖慢想出金鐘嘅人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:22:04.000Z","msg":"今日十萬人在金鐘，擋到幾耐？"},{"pid":"0406ff93ed9f2c73a22bfc53dce2e7b6e1331a44","tid":1210192,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b373b1266b6fe4f65adb6ff7013a739859ca7f6e","tid":1210192,"uid":132283,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:19:19.000Z","msg":"請問點解要拖慢想出金鐘嘅人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:22:37.000Z","msg":"留條荃灣線已經解決到問題？"},{"pid":"62c4b5c36a864f95c0536bfa6e6b36e55e1557bd","tid":1210192,"uid":44646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d863